_sText:
I'm currently working on a "possible" surf map, and this is one of the bonuses I'm making for it. A few people asked me to release it as a stand-alone bhop map, and while I were initially against, it currently seems better to get it out to the bhop community. 
The style of the map is very similar to defrag - A lot of speed, and a lot of verticality. 

Hope you enjoy it!
~Aux
